#    - Or wrap USDC → cUSDC via the frontend at https://blindference.xyz
#
# 4. Verify Setup:
#    - TypeScript: `npx @blindference/agent-sdk balance`
#
# 5. Arbitrum Sepolia Network Details:
#    - Network Name: Arbitrum Sepolia
#    - RPC URL: https://sepolia-rollup.arbitrum.io/rpc (public) or your Alchemy URL
#    - Chain ID: 421614
#    - Currency Symbol: ETH
